\\\\" style=\\\\\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: #ece9d8; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 5.4pt; width: 303.7pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; height: 51.75pt; border-top: #ece9d8; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 0cm; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt\\\\\">\r\n            <p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">取得食品生产许可证的企业应当在证书有效期内，每满<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1</span>年前的<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1</span>个月向所在嘉鱼县县质量技术监督局提出年审申请<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr style=\\\\\"height: 142.85pt; mso-yfti-irow: 8\\\\\">\r\n            <td valign=\\\\\"top\\\\\" width=\\\\\"163\\\\\" style=\\\\\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 5.4pt; width: 122.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; height: 142.85pt; border-top: #ece9d8; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 0cm; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt\\\\\">\r\n            <p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">申报材料<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td valign=\\\\\"top\\\\\" width=\\\\\"405\\\\\" style=\\\\\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: #ece9d8; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 5.4pt; width: 303.7pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; height: 142.85pt; border-top: #ece9d8; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 0cm; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt\\\\\">\r\n            <p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n            <p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">1</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">、获得食品生产许可证企业《年度自查申报表》原件<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2</span>份，在封面上加盖企业公章；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2</span>、食品生产许可证副本原件<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1</span>份，获新证企业除外；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3</span>、企业有效期内的营业执照复印件<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1</span>份；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">4</span>、年审年度内被评价为合格的比对检验结果通知单原件<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1</span>份；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5</span>、企业年度报告原件<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1</span>份；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">6</span>、企业法人或负责人的身份证复印件<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1</span>份，加盖企业公章；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">7</span>、代码证书复印件<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1</span>份；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">8</span>、《食品生产加工企业落实质量安全主体责任自查表》原件<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1</span>份，加盖企业公章。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n            <p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr style=\\\\\"height: 51.75pt; mso-yfti-lastrow: yes; mso-yfti-irow: 9\\\\\">\r\n            <td valign=\\\\\"top\\\\\" width=\\\\\"163\\\\\" style=\\\\\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 5.4pt; width: 122.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; height: 51.75pt; border-top: #ece9d8; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 0cm; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt\\\\\">\r\n            <p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">办事处理流程<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td valign=\\\\\"top\\\\\" width=\\\\\"405\\\\\" style=\\\\\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: #ece9d8; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 5.4pt; width: 303.7pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; height: 51.75pt; border-top: #ece9d8; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 0cm; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt\\\\\">\r\n            <p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">1</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">、申请<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n            <p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">企业到县质监局领取获得食品生产许可证企业年度自查申报表，并提交相关年审材料<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n            <p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">2</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">、受理<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n            <p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">企业按要求递交相关年审材料，办理部门自收到材料<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3</span>日内决定是否受理<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n            <p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">3</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">、审查<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n            <p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">（<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1</span>）办理部门应在做出受理决定后<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5</span>日内确定是否进行企业生产条件实地抽查。实地抽查按实施细则要求进行，必要时可进行抽样检验。实地抽查时间一般不超过<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1</span>日。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n            <p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">（<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2</span>）仅进行书面审查的，办理部门应在收到企业年度报告材料后<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">15</span>日内完成审查；进行实地抽查的，办理部门应在收到年度报告材料后<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">20</span>日内完成审查工作（企业整改时间不计算在内）<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n            <p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">4</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">、整改<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n            <p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">在实地抽查和实地年审中发现企业生产经营活动与《食品生产加工企业质量安全监督管理实施细则（试行）》有不符合的，应根据具体情况发出整改通知书，责令企业限期整改，整改时间最长不得超过<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1</span>个月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n            <p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">5</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">、审查结论<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n            <p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">企业年度报告审查结论分为三种<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n            <p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">（<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1</span>）合格<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n            <p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">企业生产经营全部符合规定的，企业年度报告审查结论为合格<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n            <p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">（<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2</span>）复查合格<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n            <p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">企业被责令限期整改，经整改后达到要求的，企业年度报告审查结论为复查合格<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n            <p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">（<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3</span>）复查不合格<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n            <p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">企业被责令限期整改后，仍达不到要求或者经实地抽查企业的必备生产条件或产品质量检验不合格的，企业年度报告审查结论为复查不合格<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n            <p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">6</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">、发放副本<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n            <p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">完成审查工作后<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5</span>日内通知企业领取副本</span></p>\r\n            <p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt