al\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">对于<span style=\\\\\"color: #333333\\\\\">逾期未申请办理组织机构代码登记、变更、注销、代码证书的补办、年度信息检验、换证手续的，由代码主管部门责令其限期补办，逾期不改的，将根据</span></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\">《</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">湖北省<strong><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; font-weight: normal; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold\\\\\">组织机构代码管理办法</span></strong></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\">》</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: #333333; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">湖北省人民政府令第<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">328</span>号的第十八条处以<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">500</span>元以上<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1000</span>元以下的罚款。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr style=\\\\\"height: 28.05pt; mso-yfti-irow: 10\\\\\">\r\n            <td valign=\\\\\"top\\\\\" width=\\\\\"179\\\\\" style=\\\\\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 5.4pt; width: 134.6pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; height: 28.05pt; border-top: #ece9d8; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 0cm; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt\\\\\">\r\n            <p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">办理时限<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o: